TRADE
  List commodities currently available on the open market.

SYNTAX
  trade
  trad

DESCRIPTION
  Shows all active market listings from all countries.  Each row
  shows the lot number, commodity type, amount, price per unit,
  total price, seller country, and expiration time.

  Use 'buy <lot#> <dest>' to purchase a listed lot.
  Use 'sell' to create new listings.
  Lots expire after several updates if not purchased.

EXAMPLE
  trade                     see all market listings
  buy 5 0,0                 buy lot 5 from the market

SEE ALSO
  sell  buy  commodity  nation
